1. viewportProvider was rewritten to HOC 2. removed configureStore and custom connect 3. Rewrote ScrollToTop component

features #2:
1. Creates services that get movies, tv shows and genres. 2. Movie and TV show list page main layout and functionality 3. Pagination for movieListPage layout and functionality 4. Created MovieCard and MovieList models using immutableJS (functionalty will be developed in future) 5. Made fixes and refactoring according to last review

features #3:

Created MovieItem page with its basic functionality and made it responsive 5. Includes fixes and refactoring according to first commit review
